      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Swarm和p4d之间的认证流程图。核心场景是：Swarm通过P4AS这个中间层去做SAML登录，然后p4d还要调用extension来做额外的校验。参与者从左到右依次是IdP、P4AS、Swarm、p4d和extension。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IdP",
        "P4AS",
        "Swarm",
        "p4d",
        "extension",
        "SAML"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，顺序是IdP在最左，然后是P4AS、Swarm、p4d，extension在最右。我想确认一下：Swarm是向P4AS发起SAML登录请求吗？还是直接找IdP？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Swarm",
        "P4AS",
        "IdP",
        "SAML"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Swarm先找P4AS发起SAML登录，然后P4AS再去IdP做OIDC或者SAML的登录。IdP返回认证响应给P4AS，P4AS再把SAML响应回给Swarm。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Swarm",
        "P4AS",
        "IdP",
        "SAML",
        "OIDC",
        "auth response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Swarm到P4AS的initiate SAML login画出来，然后P4AS到IdP画OIDC/SAML login。我在IdP上方加一个note，标注user authenticates。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Swarm",
        "P4AS",
        "IdP",
        "initiate SAML login",
        "OIDC/SAML login",
        "Note over I"
